to their homes.

544
00:46:01,042 --> 00:46:03,250
Obey this, instant!

545
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:09,500
Keep it together!

546
00:46:12,083 --> 00:46:14,375
Send half of the regiment
to the other side.

547
00:46:14,917 --> 00:46:16,458
