Please don't do this.

585
00:49:50,083 --> 00:49:51,667
- Come on!
- Davus!

586
00:49:52,167 --> 00:49:53,417
- Davus, no!
- Come on!

587
00:50:21,042 --> 00:50:22,583
God is one!

588
00:51:19,083 --> 00:51:23,250
Hallelujah, hallelujah, hallelujah!

